[section#make.heap
    [`make_heap]
]

[%@library make_heap]
[codeblock:declaration]
template<class RandomAccessIterator>
  constexpr void make_heap(RandomAccessIterator first, RandomAccessIterator last);

template<class RandomAccessIterator, class Compare>
  constexpr void make_heap(RandomAccessIterator first, RandomAccessIterator last,
                           Compare comp);
[codeblock:end]

[enter:description]
[para:requires]
[:en] The type of [`*first] shall satisfy the [`MoveConstructible] requirements
([#moveconstructible]) and the [`MoveAssignable] requirements
([#moveassignable]).
[:zh_CN] [`*first] 的类型应当符合 [`MoveConstructible] 的规定
（[#moveconstructible]）和 [`MoveAssignable] 的规定（[#moveassignable]）。

[para:effects]
[:en] Constructs a heap out of the range [=range(first,last)].
[:zh_CN] 将范围 [=range(first,last)] 做成一个堆。

[para:complexity]
[:en] At most [$3([`last - first])] comparisons.
[:zh_CN] 最多进行 [$3([`last - first])] 次比较。
[exit:description]
